60 Mage with epic.  14 AA's and still undecided as first skill in class.  going SCF and SCM and loving it.  Already notice the crits.  The mage is far better class 1 - 60 than a wizard. IMO  The power of a well played mage is sweet.  It is a very fun class that solo's well and with recent pet changes makes grouping even more possible.  <br>
