<br>
Pet haste cap lifted.  Now Lets come up with a better solution on defining class AA than hoping to parse greater damage than wizards who have a one shot nuke.  <br>
<br>
I for one want us to work on getting off the F'ing Modrod whore duty.<br>
<br>
**How about class AA for stackable non- lore mod rods. at 9 point cost in Class and maybe some prereq in Arch skills before hand like MB has for wiz.  You go that way it will hurt but is something worthwile... this AA will make people /drooooooooooool for the mage with it.  Wont be farming dwagons for now banked level epics--- but is a class AA I would want.<br>
<br>
** How about instant CoH AA.. non grouped of course <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ... decent refresh like every 15 min or so.  Would be a very nice skill.  Although QS and haste makes this like 5 sec...  instant is even better<br>
 <br>
